Package: healr
Title: Homeologous Exchange Automated Labeller 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Kenji", "Yip Tong", , "kenji.yiptong@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0000-6650-6918"))
Description: This package offers a series of functions to automate the process of homeologous exchange inference.
    With healr you can infer copy number ratio between homeologs, HE patterns and HE rates. 
